{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","title":"OUDSTag","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"role":"symbol"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tag is a UI element that allows to display short info like a label, keyword, or category."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Tag helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Appearances","text":"Appearances"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Status","text":"Status"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status needs to be communicated.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"completed actions or approved items."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Warning","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requiring user awareness or intervention."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}]},{"text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or contextual information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allowed when loader is activated.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Shape","type":"heading","text":"Shape"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}]},{"text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Square","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Size","type":"heading","text":"Size"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two sizes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Small"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when grouping elements visually.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Layout","type":"heading","text":"Layout"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There are four available layouts for tags:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"elements.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}]},{"text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"next to the label.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Icon","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as status, type, or action.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","text":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Version","type":"aside"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.18.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Structures"},{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(_:tableName:bundle:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appeara